  "name": "Shofar of Luck Strikes",
  "type": "equipment",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>This spiral horn has magical runes pressed into it and up to 4 charges. When you use an action to blow it, a number of creatures equal to your proficiency bonus of your choice within 600 feet of the horn and not deafened are affected. The affected creatures have their critical strike range expanded by 1 and deal one additional die of damage on a successful critical hit until the end of their next turn. The horn regains 1d4 expended charges daily at dawn.</p><p>If you expend the last charge, roll a d20. On a 1 that horn loses its magical properties and is a nonmagical horn instrument.</p>",
